text: Have you heard of transhumanism? If not, we believe that you should have. For us, transhumanism is of the utmost importance to the evolution of humanity and the continual growth of the human race due to the present, near future and long-term threats that society is facing. Transhumanism will be the key to our survival and we all need to get on board before it's too late. We're going to convince you today on why transhumanism is our last hope. Transhumanism has infinite possibilities, scientists have been creating bionic arms directly in previous animals and have even suggested the idea of digital and mit
